'''太平洋法律基金会（PLF）'''是美国一家拥有[[自由意志主義|自由意志主义]]的[[公眾利益|公众利益]]律师事务所。<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Book sources|url=https://en.wikipedia..org/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-9743665-2-8|journal=Wikipedia|language=en}}</ref>成立PLF的目的是在法庭上捍卫和促进个人和经济自由。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Giving the Right Its Day in Court|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1996-02-08-mn-33709-story.html|accessdate=2020-06-29|date=1996-02-08|last=Facebook|work=Los Angeles Times|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629051739/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1996-02-08-mn-33709-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>为此，PLF的律师为客户提供无偿的法律代理，提交[[法院之友|法庭之友]]的摘要，参与支持财产权、法律面前人人平等、言论结社自由、[[經濟自由|经济自由]]和[[權力分立|权力分立]]为目标的行政诉讼。他们已代表客户参与了14起美国最高法院审理的案件。

根据《国内收入法典》第501(c)(3)条定义，PLF是一个[[非營利組織|非盈利组织]]。它不收取法律服务费，而是由个人（53%）、基金会（17%）和协会、小企业和公司（17%）的捐款提供资金支持。除了法院判决的案件胜诉律师费外，该组织没有从政府那里得到任何资金。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Financials|url=https://pacificlegal.org/financials/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623131329/https://pacificlegal.org/financials/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Submit A Case|url=https://pacificlegal.org/submit-a-case/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701142506/https://pacificlegal.org/submit-a-case/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Donate|url=https://pacificlegal.org/donate/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701163307/https://pacificlegal.org/donate/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

该组织成立于1973年，是第一家也是历史最悠久的自由意志主义公共利益律师事务所。<ref>{{Cite book|title=By the People: Rebuilding Liberty without Permission|last=|first=Charles Murray|publisher=|year=146|isbn=|location=|pages=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title=Overruled: The Long War for Control of the U.S. Supreme Court|last=|first=|publisher=|year=|isbn=|location=|pages=}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
1973年3月5日，PLF成立于[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[沙加緬度_(加利福尼亞州)|沙加缅度市]]，其最初的员工主要由当时州长罗纳德·里根（Ronald Reagan）的福利改革团队的成员组成。<ref name=":0" />前10个月的拟议预算为11.7万美元，在第一任主席罗纳德·祖姆布伦（Ronald a.Zumbrun）的指导下，公共福利基金的律师于1973年6月开始了诉讼活动。<ref name=":0" />目前，PLF在美国拥有超过30名律师和4个办事处，分别位于：加利福尼亚州沙加缅度、弗吉尼亚州阿灵顿、佛罗里达州棕滨园和华盛顿州西雅图。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Staff|url=https://pacificlegal.org/staff/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623131354/https://pacificlegal.org/staff/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Meet the Bellevue Libertarians Who Are Fighting Seattle's Progressive Housing Laws|url=https://www.thestranger.com/features/2017/04/05/25056578/meet-the-bellevue-libertarians-who-are-fighting-seattles-progressive-housing-laws|accessdate=2020-06-29|last=Groover|first=Heidi|work=The Stranger|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805084538/https://www.thestranger.com/features/2017/04/05/25056578/meet-the-bellevue-libertarians-who-are-fighting-seattles-progressive-housing-laws|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 法律范畴 ==

=== 财产权 ===
PLF的产权案件主要集中在财产限制使用和[[环境法学|环境法学]]方面。基金会的律师已经在[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]成功地为五个财产限制案件辩护：诺兰诉加利福尼亚海岸委员会、苏特姆诉塔霍地区规划署、帕拉佐洛诉罗德岛、昆茨诉圣约翰河水管理区、尼克诉宾夕法尼亚州斯科特镇。

PLF在下级法院就住房和分区问题提起诉讼。PLF成功地挑战了旧金山的“搬迁援助支付条例”，该条例要求房东向房客支付费用，帮房客获得新的住所。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Levin v. City and County of San Francisco|url=https://pacificlegal.org/case/levin-v-city-and-county-of-san-francisco/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507185347/https://pacificlegal.org/case/levin-v-city-and-county-of-san-francisco/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=San Francisco fails in assault on Pacific Legal Foundation’s big court win for local landlords|url=https://www.citizensjournal.us/san-francisco-fails-in-assault-on-pacific-legal-foundations-big-court-win-for-local-landlords/|accessdate=2020-06-29|date=2017-03-20|last=Tash|first=Debra|work=Citizens Journal|archive-date=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630182012/https://www.citizensjournal.us/san-francisco-fails-in-assault-on-pacific-legal-foundations-big-court-win-for-local-landlords/|dead-url=no}}</ref>PLF在密歇根州最高法院有一个未决案件，挑战一种常见的实操：如果未支付税费，县级政府会取消所有者对地产的赎回权，保留额外的房屋净值。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Michigan Supreme Court To Hear Case On Alleged Tax Foreclosure Abuse|url=https://detroit.cbslocal.com/2018/12/31/michigan-supreme-court-to-hear-case-on-alleged-tax-foreclosure-abuse/|accessdate=2020-06-29|date=2018-12-31|last=srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e59fae2731a2716e650f90d37942af82?s=84|first=<img alt='' src='https://i1 wp com/pbs twimg com/profile_images/1071250524291293184/juOPypC6_normal jpg?resize=42%2C42'|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507185348/https://detroit.cbslocal.com/2018/12/31/michigan-supreme-court-to-hear-case-on-alleged-tax-foreclosure-abuse/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

PLF的环境法诉讼经常涉及到根据《清洁水法案》或《濒危物种法》对私人财产的联邦监管提出挑战，在美国最高法院赢得五个案件的胜利。在康托斯基诉斯嘉丽案中，一名明尼苏达州的地产商被剥夺了在其地产上建造房屋的权利，<ref>{{Cite web|title=CONTOSKI v. SCARLETT {{!}} Civil No. 05-2528 (JRT/RLE). {{!}} D. Minn. {{!}} Judgment {{!}} Law {{!}} CaseMine|url=https://www.casemine.com/judgement/us/5914708dadd7b0493435f1e7|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=www.casemine.com|language=en|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327200250/https://www.casemine.com/judgement/us/5914708dadd7b0493435f1e7|dead-url=no}}</ref>一个导致秃鹰从濒危物种名单上消失的案例。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bald Eagle Delisting|url=https://www.fws.gov/pacific/ecoservices/BaldEagleDelisting.htm|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=www.fws.gov|archive-date=2020-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200420015703/https://www.fws.gov/pacific/ecoservices/BaldEagleDelisting.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>PLF认为，[[美國魚類及野生動物管理局|美国鱼类及野生动物管理局]]在得出秃鹰种群已经恢复的结论后，没有将秃鹰从名单上除名。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The bald eagle still flying high|url=https://pacificlegal.org/the-bald-eagle-still-flying-high/|accessdate=2020-06-29|date=2010-12-20|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507185640/https://pacificlegal.org/the-bald-eagle-still-flying-high/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=govinfo|url=https://www.govinfo.gov/app/details/FR-1999-07-06/99-16924|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=www.govinfo.gov|language=en|archive-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507185643/https://www.govinfo.gov/app/details/FR-1999-07-06/99-16924|dead-url=no}}</ref>

PLF代表安迪·约翰逊（Andy Johnson）参与环境保护局的纠纷案件。约翰逊在怀俄明州的地产上建了一个蓄水池，为他的牛提供水源。美国环保局认为他违反了《清洁水法案》，要求他清除水塘，并对他处以每天3.75万美元的罚款，总计罚款额为1,600万美元。<ref>{{Cite web|title=5-year fight with EPA finally over for Wyoming man and his pond|url=https://www.deseret.com/2016/5/11/20588360/5-year-fight-with-epa-finally-over-for-wyoming-man-and-his-pond|accessdate=2020-06-29|date=2016-05-11|last=Cabrero|first=Alex|work=Deseret News|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031190741/https://www.deseret.com/2016/5/11/20588360/5-year-fight-with-epa-finally-over-for-wyoming-man-and-his-pond|dead-url=no}}</ref>怀俄明州的参议员称该机构的做法是“严厉的官僚作风”。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Family Pond Boils at Center of a ‘Regulatory War’ in Wyoming|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/19/us/regulatory-war-fought-over-a-wyoming-familys-pond.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2015-09-18|accessdate=2020-06-29|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Jack|last=Healy|archive-date=2020-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226191703/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/19/us/regulatory-war-fought-over-a-wyoming-familys-pond.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>该案于2016年结案，环保局撤销了罚款和要求，约翰逊同意种植柳树保护土地不受侵蚀。<ref>{{Cite web|title=EPA settles with Wyoming farmer over man-made pond|url=https://thehill.com/policy/energy-environment/279421-epa-settles-water-pollution-case-with-wyoming-farmer|accessdate=2020-06-29|date=2016-05-10|last=Cama|first=Timothy|work=TheHill|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627230304/https://thehill.com/policy/energy-environment/279421-epa-settles-water-pollution-case-with-wyoming-farmer|dead-url=no}}</ref>特朗普总统签署行政命令，降低监管机构对公民执法进行辩护的时候依赖行政指导，并就此强调了约翰逊的案件。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Opinion {{!}} No More Rule by Memorandum|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/no-more-rule-by-memorandum-11570663050|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|date=2019-10-09|accessdate=2020-06-29|issn=0099-9660|language=en-US|first=The Editorial|last=Board|archive-date=2020-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125174041/https://www.wsj.com/articles/no-more-rule-by-memorandum-11570663050|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Trump highlights Wyoming man's battle against EPA during White House ceremony|url=https://bridgervalleypioneer.com/article/trump-highlights-wyoming-mans-battle-against-epa-during-white-house-ceremony|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Bridger Valley Pioneer|archive-date=2019-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031190743/https://bridgervalleypioneer.com/article/trump-highlights-wyoming-mans-battle-against-epa-during-white-house-ceremony|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Remarks by President Trump at Signing of Executive Orders on Transparency in Federal Guidance and Enforcement|url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/remarks-president-trump-signing-executive-orders-transparency-federal-guidance-enforcement/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=The White House|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711161542/https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/remarks-president-trump-signing-executive-orders-transparency-federal-guidance-enforcement/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

PLF代表密歇根州居民尤里·拉发里（Uri Rafaeli），他的地产的赎回权被取消了，在拍卖会拍卖的金额包含支付8.41美元的房产税负债。该县保留了拍卖所得的全部收入，金额超过24,000美元。PLF在密歇根州最高法院出庭，对一项旨在防止损失的州法律提出质疑，该法律允许各县保留房地产拍卖的全部收益，即使拍卖所得的金额大于所欠的税额。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Man Loses Home After Failing To Pay $8.41 In Property Taxes|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/kellyphillipserb/2019/12/06/man-loses-home-after-failing-to-pay-841-in-property-taxes/|accessdate=2020-06-29|last=Erb|first=Kelly Phillips|work=Forbes|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731000457/https://www.forbes.com/sites/kellyphillipserb/2019/12/06/man-loses-home-after-failing-to-pay-841-in-property-taxes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>这种被PLF称为“房屋净值盗窃”的做法在其他州（包括[[亞利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]、[[麻薩諸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]和[[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]]）也是合法的。PLF计划通过法院系统废除这些法律或鼓励立法改革。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Unpaid $8.41 property tax bill cost Michigan man his house|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/unpaid-property-taxes-cost-michigan-residents-their-house/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=www.cbsnews.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214145332/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/unpaid-property-taxes-cost-michigan-residents-their-house/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Southfield man underpaid his property taxes by $8.41, lost home and money|url=https://www.metrotimes.com/news-hits/archives/2019/11/06/southfield-man-underpaid-his-property-taxes-by-841-lost-home-and-money|accessdate=2020-06-29|last=Kalil-Barrino|first=Marisa|work=Detroit Metro Times|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805015146/https://www.metrotimes.com/news-hits/archives/2019/11/06/southfield-man-underpaid-his-property-taxes-by-841-lost-home-and-money|dead-url=no}}</ref>

PLF经常参与海岸线之间的地产纠纷诉讼案件，包括数起对加州海岸委员会的行为提出质疑的诉讼案件。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Lent v. California Coastal Commission|url=https://pacificlegal.org/case/lent-v-california-coastal-commission/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2019-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191231180829/https://pacificlegal.org/case/lent-v-california-coastal-commission/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Wall v. Cal. Coastal Commission|url=https://pacificlegal.org/case/wall-v-cal-coastal-commission/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617193210/https://pacificlegal.org/case/wall-v-cal-coastal-commission/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Greene v. California Coastal Commission|url=https://pacificlegal.org/case/greene-v-california-coastal-commission/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2019-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191231180829/https://pacificlegal.org/case/greene-v-california-coastal-commission/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Zito v. North Carolina Coastal Resource Commission; Town of Nags Head|url=https://pacificlegal.org/case/zito-v-north-carolina-coastal-resource-commission-town-of-nags-head/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617201928/https://pacificlegal.org/case/zito-v-north-carolina-coastal-resource-commission-town-of-nags-head/|dead-url=no}}</ref>该组织辩称，海岸线的私人所有权与公共利益之间不存在冲突，因为开发可以增加海滩的体验，还能保护海滩。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Legal property rights owners make our coasts more beautiful|url=https://pacificlegal.org/property-owners-with-strong-property-rights-make-our-coasts-more-beautiful/|accessdate=2020-06-29|date=2019-12-20|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2020-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407234403/https://pacificlegal.org/property-owners-with-strong-property-rights-make-our-coasts-more-beautiful/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 经济自由 ===
PLF认为某些许可法律和类似法规侵犯了个人谋生的权利，导致失业，降低美国人生活水平。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Economic Liberty|url=https://pacificlegal.org/cases-category/economic-liberty/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200618024646/https://pacificlegal.org/cases-category/economic-liberty/|dead-url=no}}</ref>PLF在多个州与需求证明（CON）法律抗争，该法律要求新进入就业市场的人从政府获得“需求证明”，目前涉及这些行业的企业可能会反对他们进入行业引起竞争。<ref>{{Cite web|title=“Certificates of Public Convenience and Necessity” for moving companies: the Competitor’s Veto|url=https://pacificlegal.org/certificate-of-public-convenience-and-necessity-the-competitors-veto/|accessdate=2020-06-29|date=2013-11-17|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327221907/https://pacificlegal.org/certificate-of-public-convenience-and-necessity-the-competitors-veto/|dead-url=no}}</ref>PLF代表几家搬家公司挑战其所在州的需求证明法律。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Federal judge rules in favor of Wildcat Moving in its battle to overturn 'anti-competitive' state law|url=https://www.kentucky.com/news/business/article44469750.html|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215065632/https://www.kentucky.com/news/business/article44469750.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>PLF代表劳埃德运输和储存公司的阿蒂·沃格特（Arty Vogt）质疑西弗吉尼亚州管理州际搬运工的需求证明法，法案要求该州新的搬家公司的成立必须得到现任搬家公司的批准。该案于2017年结案，当时该州通过了一项法律，有效地废除了该条例。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Finally, a right to move — and to compete — in West Virginia|url=https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/finally-a-right-to-move-mdash-and-to-compete-mdash-in-west-virginia|accessdate=2020-06-29|date=2017-07-05|work=Washington Examiner|language=en|archive-date=2019-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723191736/https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/finally-a-right-to-move-mdash-and-to-compete-mdash-in-west-virginia|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年，PLF在肯塔基州提起诉讼，质疑该州监管的非紧急医疗运输的需求证明法。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Legacy Medical Transport, LLC and Phillip Truesdell v. Adam Meier, et al.|url=https://pacificlegal.org/case/legacy-medical-transport-v-adam-meier/|accessdate=2020-06-29|work=Pacific Legal Foundation|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607183046/https://pacificlegal.org/case/legacy-medical-transport-v-adam-meier/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2008年，PLF赢得了梅里菲尔德诉洛克伊尔案，这是对加利福尼亚州有害生物控制许可的质疑。[[美国联邦第九巡回上诉法院|美国联邦第九巡回上诉法院]]裁定：“为了自身利益而采取的经济保护主义，无论其与共同利益的关系如何，都不能说是在促进政府的合法利益。”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Big Victory for Economic Liberty|url=https://www.cato.org/blog/big-victory-economic-liberty|accessdate=2020-06-29|date=2008-09-22|work=Cato Institute|language=en|archive-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507184518/https://www.cato.org/blog/big-victory-economic-liberty|dead-url=no}}</ref>

