erature-science-drama-music-art-and-finance/oclc/474896671|date=1865|journal=The nation : a weekly journal devoted to politics, literature, science, drama, music, art, and finance.|language=en|issn=0027-8378|access-date=2020-06-29|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701012651/https://www.worldcat.org/title/nation-a-weekly-journal-devoted-to-politics-literature-science-drama-music-art-and-finance/oclc/474896671|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Suit Challenges Sheff Magnet-School Lottery Process|url=https://www.courant.com/news/connecticut/hc-news-magnet-lottery-lawsuit-20180215-story.html|accessdate=2020-06-29|last=Kauffman|first=Matthew|work=courant.com|archive-date=2019-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509164319/https://www.courant.com/news/connecticut/hc-news-magnet-lottery-lawsuit-20180215-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

